          <p>You will be staying in a boutique style hotel Located in beautiful Sea Point suburb of Cape Town with the ocean view and palm trees right by your door step. </p>
          <p><i class="fas fa-thumbtack"></i>12mins walk to Clifton & Camps bay beach</p>
          <p><i class="fas fa-thumbtack"></i>1min walk to Atlantic seaboard</p>
          <p><i class="fas fa-thumbtack"></i>20 mins drive to airport</p>
